commandDescription: Command to compare two organization to get the differences. Return the metadata that exists on target but not exists on source
sourceFlagDescription: Source Salesforce org to compare. If you want to compare your active org with other, this options is not necessary because use the --root option for get the project's auth org. If you choose source, --root will be ignored
csvFlagDescription: Option to show the result as CSV instead a table if not select --json flag
noDataToShowError: Not metadata types found to describe
